title: Live updates: Florida Gators lead Missouri in second half
text:
Live updates: Florida Gators lead Missouri in second half Florida Gators v Missouri Ed Zurga / Getty Images 
Jim McElwain head coach of the Florida Gators leads members of team into Memorial Stadium for warm ups prior to a game against the Missouri Tigers. 
Jim McElwain head coach of the Florida Gators leads members of team into Memorial Stadium for warm ups prior to a game against the Missouri Tigers. (Ed Zurga / Getty Images) 
The Gators look for to end the Tigers' two-game win streak in the series.
